graph TB
    subgraph AutoGluonServer["KServe AutoGluon Server"]
        direction TB
        MainEntry["__main__.py<br/>Entry Point"]
        PredictorFactory["predictor_factory.py<br/>Predictor Factory"]
        PredictorDetect["predictor_detect.py<br/>Auto-Detection"]
        TabularModel["tabular_model.py<br/>TabularPredictor<br/>(v1 + v2 OIP)"]
        TimeSeriesModel["timeseries_model.py<br/>TimeSeriesPredictor<br/>(v1 only)"]
        ModelRepo["AutoGluonModelRepository<br/>Multi-Model Support"]
        RuntimePaths["runtime_paths.py<br/>Writable Path Setup"]

        MainEntry -->|creates| PredictorFactory
        PredictorFactory -->|uses| PredictorDetect
        PredictorDetect -->|detects type| TabularModel
        PredictorDetect -->|detects type| TimeSeriesModel
        MainEntry -->|optional| ModelRepo
        ModelRepo -->|scans & loads| PredictorFactory
        MainEntry -->|initializes| RuntimePaths
    end

    subgraph KServeSDK["KServe SDK (Framework)"]
        ModelServer["kserve.ModelServer<br/>FastAPI + gRPC"]
        V1Endpoints["v1 REST Endpoints<br/>8080/TCP"]
        V2Endpoints["v2 OIP Endpoints<br/>8080/TCP"]
        GRPCServer["gRPC Server<br/>8081/TCP"]
        HealthChecks["Health & Readiness<br/>Probes"]

        ModelServer --> V1Endpoints
        ModelServer --> V2Endpoints
        ModelServer --> GRPCServer
        ModelServer --> HealthChecks
    end

    subgraph KServeStorage["kserve-storage"]
        StorageLib["Storage Download<br/>S3 / GCS / PVC / URI"]
    end

    Client[External Client] -->|POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>POST /v2/models/model/infer| ModelServer
    MainEntry -->|registers model| ModelServer
    TabularModel -->|implements| ModelServer
    TimeSeriesModel -->|implements| ModelServer

    StorageInitializer["Storage Initializer<br/>(Init Container)"] -->|downloads to /mnt/models| StorageLib
    StorageLib -->|model artifacts| PredictorFactory

    KServeController["KServe Controller<br/>(Operator)"] -->|deploys pod| AutoGluonServer
    IstioSidecar["Istio Sidecar<br/>(Envoy)"] -->|mTLS proxy| ModelServer
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes /metrics| ModelServer

